<i>adverb</i>: 평온히 [평온히], 잔잔히 [잔잔히], 담담히 [담ː담히], 고요히 [고요히] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>평온히 [평온히]</dt><br>
<dd>calmly; quietly; serenely</dd><br>
<dd>걱정이나 탈이 없고 조용하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Quietly without any worries or troubles.</dd><br>
<dt>잔잔히 [잔잔히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. calmly; tranquilly; quietly</dd><br>
<dd>바람이나 물결 등이 심하지 않고 움직임이 거의 없이.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of the wind, a wave, etc., being still and not severe.</dd><br>
<dd>2. serenely; tranquilly; calmly</dd><br>
<dd>분위기가 고요하고 평화롭게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of an atmosphere being silent and peaceful.</dd><br>
<dd>3. calmly; serenely</dd><br>
<dd>표정이나 태도 등이 차분하고 평온하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of one's look, attitude, etc., being composed and peaceful.</dd><br>
<dd>4. gently</dd><br>
<dd>소리가 조용하고 부드럽게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of a sound being quiet and soft.</dd><br>
<dt>담담히 [담ː담히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. composedly; calmly</dd><br>
<dd>차분하고 편안하게.</dd><br>
<dd>With a calm and comfortable attitude.</dd><br>
<dd>2. plainly</dd><br>
<dd>글이나 말 내용이 감정적이지 않고 객관적이게.</dd><br>
<dd>Objectively, not expressing oneself emotionally in writing or speaking.</dd><br>
<dd>3. serenely</dd><br>
<dd>물이 맑고 그 움직임이 고요하고 평온하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state such as that when clean water flows quietly and peacefully.</dd><br>
<dd>4. plainly</dd><br>
<dd>맛이 짜거나 느끼하지 않고 산뜻하고 싱겁게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of tasting fresh and insipid, not salty or greasy.</dd><br>
<dt>고요히 [고요히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. silently</dd><br>
<dd>시끄럽거나 어지럽지 않고 조용하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Quietly, neither noisily nor confusedly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. serenely; calmly</dd><br>
<dd>강이나 바다 등의 물결이 잔잔하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of a river, the sea, etc., flowing with small ripples.</dd><br>
<dd>3. peacefully; serenely</dd><br>
<dd>마음이나 상태 등이 조용하고 평화롭게.</dd><br>
<dd>With a quiet and peaceful mind or in such a state.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>